title: Impostor Syndrome
abstract: 70% of all people experience "impostor syndrome" at least once in their life. In this workshop we will explore the phenomenon and the feeling in ourselves and in group setting by discussing and trying out some of the techniques that have been found useful in countering the paralyzing effects.
